Description: Bundled Node.js runtime for Fidus Writer
 This package provides a bundled Node.js runtime (via nodejs-wheel)
 for Fidus Writer on systems where the distribution's Node.js package
 is too old (below version 22).
 .
 The main fiduswriter-server package prefers the system nodejs (>= 22)
 if available. This package is only installed automatically on older
 distributions that do not meet that requirement.
 .
 On systems with nodejs (>= 22) already installed, this package is
 not needed and will not be installed.
